com.tgerm.tolerado.axis14.core
Class ToleradoStubRegistry

java.lang.Object
  com.tgerm.tolerado.axis14.core.ToleradoStubRegistry

public class ToleradoStubRegistry
extends java.lang.Object

A central registry/cache for ToleradoStub, ToleradoMetaStub and ToleradoApexStub. This class gives methods like getPartnerStub(Credential) to quickly get either a cached or first time logged in Tolerado Stub impl. In case one don't want cached stub and want to force login, then call this one getPartnerStub(Credential, boolean) with last boolean param as true

Author:
abhinav
